OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FCloudy with patchy light rain
OL,6,Farriving across the region from late
OL,7,Fmorning. Some places remaining dry
OL,8,Fbefore skies break and sunny spells
OL,9,Fdevelop into the afternoon. Becoming
OL,10,Frather breezy.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,13,FBlustery with sunny spells and heavy
OL,14,Fshowers on both Wednesday and
OL,15,FThursday. More settled on Friday with
OL,16,Fdrier and brighter conditions.
OL,17,FRemaining chilly, with a risk of frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
